<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type'/>
</head>
<body>
<h3>Password Reset for <%= @user.email %></h3>

<p>
  Hi <%= @user.first_name %>, you are receiving this email because you requested a password reset. To reset your
  password, please visit the link below.
</p>
<%= link_to "Reset Your Password", "#{edit_password_url}?user_information=#{URI.encode_www_form_component(@user_information)}" %>
<p>
  If you didn't ask to change your password, don't worry! Your password is still safe and you can delete this
  email.
</p>

<p>-The OneFeed Team</p>
</body>
</html>